trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman"></xref> class and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellman"> </xref> klasse og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method executes in two distinct scenarios: - If `disposing` equals `true`, the method has been called directly or indirectly by a user's code.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden utfører i to ulike scenarioer: – Hvis `disposing` er lik `true`, metoden er kalt direkte eller indirekte av en brukers kode.

trans-unit.source: Managed and unmanaged resources can be disposed.
trans-unit.target: Administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser kan være fjernet.

trans-unit.source: - If `disposing` equals `false`, the method has been called by the runtime from inside the finalizer, and you should not reference managed resources.
trans-unit.target: -Hvis `disposing` er lik `false`metoden er kalt med kjøretiden i sluttbehandleren, og du kan ikke referere til administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Only unmanaged resources can be disposed.
trans-unit.target: Bare uforvaltede ressurser kan være fjernet.

trans-unit.source: If you need to provide cleanup code for managed and unmanaged resources that an object created, you should override this method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du trenger ikke angi oppryddingskode for behandlet ressurser som et objekt opprettes, må du overstyre denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()`method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()`metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` -parameteren er SANN, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey>referanser.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.ECDiffieHellmanPublicKey>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
